{"tid":49720,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"LG V20 Bootloop 再現？LG：廉價 Type-C 線惹的禍","createTime":"2016-12-22T02:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T09:59:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99ffac9f2c0ba4eba644839b19aa873ec4f18bfe","tid":49720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:04:33.000Z","msg":"LG V20 都有 Bootloop 問題？<br />\n<br />\n據韓國傳媒報導，有小部分 LG V20 用家在網上發文表示，手上的 LG V20 突現出現不斷重新開機問題，情況同之前 G4、V10 的 Bootloop 類似。<br />\n<br />\n但到底點解會咁呢？據韓國維修中心方面的人員解釋，就話係因為用咗平價的第三方 Type-C 線幫 V20 充電而導致。無論呢個講法準確與否，睇黎各位 V20 用家，都係盡量用番原廠 Type-C 線及充電器為妙。"},{"pid":"e7839e97549583aca7afa13e82a9dd930e5d165a","tid":49720,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劈價未"},{"pid":"29bcfb4e42856198c822641b7d45178c870ed5a8","tid":49720,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc717084079f17fc8671898999b0b554e993104","tid":49720,"uid":61805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"學三星， 告返個客"},{"pid":"7b53f462233e6dbe1ea543dee177227cac337ada","tid":49720,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦，用返原裝咪又咁<br />\n<br />\n永不錄用LG"},{"pid":"8d25cee76f78925fcd238b5c44e9cd264bafbced","tid":49720,"uid":8294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛用埋lg拖板制面？"},{"pid":"4fe4c79e04e613e2bb7d41730707aa81b5a2359e","tid":49720,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"其實今時今日買LG呢啲垃圾都唔係弱智咁簡單"},{"pid":"54837e67177437ce1a275e2d1b545684192ee673","tid":49720,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"泡菜仔好鐘意瀨人<img